| **Monitoring Tools** | Grafana, Prometheus, ELK Stack            |


| **Tool**             | **Purpose**                                                      |
| -------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Dash/Streamlit**   | Building interactive dashboards for real-time data visualization |
| **Grafana**          | Real-time monitoring and visualization of time series data       |
| **Power BI/Tableau** | Business-oriented analytics and reporting                        |



| **Category**         | **Tools/Practices**                                                                    |
| -------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Unit Testing**     | Pytest, unittest                                                                       |
